{"type":"message","id":"5da06a05","parentId":"b3e30bc4","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:06:17.361Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me read the most recent pulse log.","thinkingSignature":"d40b955382637849e2941533c26915d89f981b4c20bbf1dbf0828e4e565360b3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_f4jr0vblh14t_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\memory\\session\\pulse_2026-03-24 010505.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":662,"output":63,"cacheRead":11954,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12679,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774328775078}}
{"type":"message","id":"36052c40","parentId":"5da06a05","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:06:17.370Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_f4jr0vblh14t_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿# Pulse: 2026-03-24 010505\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: tic/classifier.ps1 (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me analyze the current state and determine the best next action.\r\n\r\nCurrent situation:\r\n- Phase 0 and Phase 1 analysis are complete\r\n- Key insight: Compression and Causal Discovery are the SAME problem\r\n- Next action: Implement TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment\r\n- Pending: Implement TIC classifier on pulse logs, measure classification accuracy, predict next pulse content\r\n\r\nThe most concrete next step is to start implementing the TIC experiment. I need to:\r\n1. Access the pulse logs\r\n2. Implement a classifier that identifies invariant vs variant content\r\n3. Test prediction of next pulse\r\n\r\nLet me first check what pulse logs exist and their structure, then implement the TIC classifier.\r\n\r\nLooking at the notes, the last pulse was `pulse_2026-03-24 010221.md`. Let me check what logs exist and implement the TIC classifier.\r\n\r\nFor the TIC experiment, I should:\r\n1. First understand the structure of pulse logs\r\n2. Implement a simple classifier\r\n3. Run it on the last N pulse logs\r\n\r\nLet me create a script that implements TIC classifier. The key insight is that invariant structure = causal structure. So I need to:\r\n- Identify patterns that persist across pulses (invariants)\r\n- Identify patterns that change (variants)\r\n- Use invariants to predict next pulse\r\n\r\nLet me start by examining the logs directory structure and then implementing the TIC classifier.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the logical next step to validate the compression-causal duality hypothesis. Need to examine pulse log structure and implement the invariant/variant classifier.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nExamine pulse logs to understand their structure, then implement the TIC classifier script that will:\r\n1. Extract temporal patterns across recent pulses\r\n2. Classify content as invariant (persists) vs variant (changes)\r\n3. Attempt to predict next pulse content from invariants\r\n4. Output classification accuracy metrics\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n`\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) Classifier\r\n# Tests hypothesis: causal structure = invariant structure\r\n# Success criteria: >70% invariant/variant classification, >60% next-pulse prediction\r\n\r\nparam(\r\n    [int]$Lookback = 5,\r\n    [float]$Threshold = 0.6\r\n)\r\n\r\n$ErrorActionPreference = \"Stop\"\r\n$ScriptDir = Split-Path -Parent $MyInvocation.MyCommand.Path\r\n$RootDir = Split-Path -Parent $ScriptDir\r\n\r\n# --- Phase 1: Extract patterns from pulse logs ---\r\nWrite-Host \"=== TIC: Temporal Invariance Compression Experiment ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\nWrite-Host \"Lookback: $Lookback pulses\" -ForegroundColor Gray\r\n\r\n$logFiles = Get-ChildItem -Path \"$RootDir/logs\" -Filter \"pulse_*.md\" | \r\n    Sort-Object Name -Descending | \r\n    Select-Object -First $Lookback\r\n\r\nif ($logFiles.Count -lt 3) {\r\n    Write-Host \"Insufficient pulse logs for TIC experiment (need at least 3)\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\r\n    exit 0\r\n}\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"Found $($logFiles.Count) pulse logs\" -ForegroundColor Gray\r\n\r\n# Extract content blocks from each pulse\r\nfunction Get-PulseBlocks($file) {\r\n    $content = Get-Content $file.FullName -Raw\r\n    # Extract sections: OBSERVATION, ACTION, MUTATION, content\r\n    $blocks = @{}\r\n    \r\n    if ($content -match '(?s)### OBSERVATION\\s*\\n(.*?)(?=###|\\z)') {\r\n        $blocks['observation'] = $matches[1].Trim()\r\n    }\r\n    if ($content -match '(?s)### ACTION\\s*\\n(.*?)(?=###|\\z)') {\r\n        $blocks['action'] = $matches[1].Trim()\r\n    }\r\n    if ($content -match '(?s)### MUTATION\\s*\\n(.*?)```') {\r\n        $blocks['mutation'] = $matches[1].Trim()\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    # Count words/lines as simple content metrics\r\n    $blocks['wordcount'] = ($content -split '\\s+' | Where-Object { $_ -ne '' }).Count\r\n    $blocks['linecount'] = ($content -split \"`n\" | Where-Object { $_ -match '\\S' }).Count\r\n    \r\n    return $blocks\r\n}\r\n\r\n# --- Phase 2: Compute invariant/variant metrics ---\r\nWrite-Host \"`n--- Computing Invariant/Variant Classification ---\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\r\n\r\n$allBlocks = $logFiles | ForEach-Object { Get-PulseBlocks $_ }\r\n$allBlocks += @{ timestamp = \"aggregate\" }\r\n\r\n# Simple invariant detection: content that appears in ALL pulses\r\n$allObservations = $allBlocks | Where-Object { $_.observation } | ForEach-Object { $_.observation }\r\n$allActions = $allBlocks | Where-Object { $_.action } | ForEach-Object { $_.action }\r\n\r\n# Word frequency analysis\r\n$allText = ($allBlocks | Where-Object { $_.observation -or $_.action } | ForEach-Object { \r\n    $_.observation + \" \" + $_.action \r\n}) -join \" \"\r\n\r\n$words = $allText.ToLower() -split '\\W+' | Where-Object { $_.Length -gt 3 }\r\n$wordCounts = $words | Group-Object | Sort-Object Count -Descending\r\n\r\n# Invariant words: appear in majority of pulses\r\n$pulseCount = $Lookback\r\n$invariantWords = $wordCounts | Where-Object { $_.Count -ge ($pulseCount * $Threshold) } | Select-Object -First 20\r\n\r\nWrite-Host \"INVARIANT WORDS (appear in >= $($Threshold*100)% of pulses):\" -ForegroundColor Green\r\n$invariantWords | ForEach-Object { \r\n   \n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 0\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 01:05:39\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774328777368}}
